<1ST_LINE>r a AM-DigestBriefs     08-20 1444</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Digest Briefs,1505</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: This package does not contain the following items from the
News Digest: HAIFA, Israel _ Israel-Explosion; WASH _ US-Pakistan;
WARSAW, Poland _ Poland; UNDATED _ Political Rdp; OMAGH, Northern
